/*----------------------------------------------------------------------
--  Rule 1
--
--  Justification:
--    The proof function prf_isAlarming models and is equivalent to the
--    proof function Alarm.Interface.prf_isAlarming.
--    The abstract own variable Output of Alarm (the parameter of IsAlarming)
--    is refined into the single component Alarm.Interface.Output.
----------------------------------------------------------------------*/
alarm_user(1): prf_isalarming(Op) may_be_replaced_by
                 alarm__interface__prf_isalarming(fld_alarm__interface__output(Op)) .

